series.description:
A series of song contests for Project SEKAI COLORFUL STAGE! feat. Hatsune Miku.

Winning songs get recorded in the game as a playable song (in 2D mode). 
Winners also appear in the game credits and receive an Amazon gift card worth 50,000yen.

List of winning entries can be found [here](https://vocadb.net/L/10219).

series.description:
Host: [TILDECHU](https://vocadb.net/Ar/150543)
SleepyFesta! Beta has 7 periods lasting until the release date of the Hatsune Miku fan-made childrens' game "Lovely! Miku Sweet Slumber". It is a song festival where entering Vocaloid Producers create and submit songs to celebrate a specific character of their choice. A period in SleepyFesta is just a reccomended character, but you can choose any. By the end of the festival, a raffle is held for each character. The chosen song for the raffle is the character's theme song. Use the tag #SLEEPFES2025 to announce that it is a entry song.
series.name: SleepyFesta! Beta
